+-------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Treatment 1 | DMSO control                                                                                                                                                                                              |
+-------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
